{"tid":29966,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[持續進修]打算整個PC application有冇好介紹","createTime":"2016-12-09T02:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T06:27:03.000Z","uid":61565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f02af0a59d854f202d41ab20c066a83f0a62193","tid":29966,"uid":61565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T02:21:02.000Z","msg":"各位巴/絲好<br />\n<br />\n小弟諗住進修一下Programming技術, 諗住整一個PC APP同Mobile app, 再用SERVER去同步資料同埋做notification<br />\n<br />\n但我唔多清楚用咩做PC application(自己用開WINDOW FORM, 但今次想SUPPORT埋OSX), 想睇下有咩framework同language好用, 求各指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時會用以下LANGUAGE:<br />\nPC: (諗緊JAVAFX, 但未用過唔知好唔好用)<br />\nMOBILE: IOS(SWIFT)<br />\nServer: python (有冇邊隻FRAMEWORK好用)<br />\nDB: MONGODB<br />\n<br />\n大部份都用D未用過既LANGUAGE去做, 如果有咩建議, 求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3bab035348aac43334fc70bf96644e407c2506","tid":29966,"uid":1573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:09:19.000Z","msg":"有寫過web既可以諗下用JavaScript<br />\nFrontend: React / Vue.js<br />\nMobile: React Native / Weex<br />\nDesktop: Electron<br />\nServer: Node.js<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.github.io/react/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.github.io%2Freact%2F&d=vkb9cU1le4sf79eUvImRpgv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=4b4fc209\" target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.github.io/react/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.github.io/react-native/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%